\par\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\sa360\sl264\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 You are now ready to begin your own project\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 go to }{\f1\fs22\b1\i0\cf4 <$Scr_Cs::0>File > New Project<!$Scr_Cs::0>}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  to get going. Happy writing!}}